<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢٧٣) و <span class="c1">" الإرواء "</span> <span class="c2">(١٥٤٧)</span> .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
